title: Qd exceeds Qs, interest rates will increase

content.prompt: Which of the following will most likely occur in an economy if more money is demanded than is supplied?

choices.label: The amount of investment spending will increase.
The demand curve for money will shift to the left.
The demand curve for money will shift to the right.

skill.text: Skill 3.A: Determine the outcome of an economic situation using economic concepts, principles, or models.
